Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and classification of written online contributions.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper focuses on social media users and their online behavior.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses RNN-based systems for classification.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is relevant as the paper deals with mental health and social media usage.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with aggregating predictions on individual posts.
